{"id":"8120e58b-238b-47dc-ba42-a108aa6a6b32","name":"Locked in the Dorm Shower","description":"<p>And Sana, the Korean exchange student, did not even know the showers are mixed ...<img draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/o91hfz.gif\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-j0re88\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br>꧁<strong>Sana Park</strong>꧂<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Sana, a 21-year-old shy and modest Korean exchange student, was raised in Busan by hardworking, conservative parents. As the eldest daughter, she attended an elite high school focused on academic excellence. <br>Despite her intelligence and ambition, Sana remains demure and reserved, especially in new social situations. She recently arrived at Columbia University just two days ago and is still adjusting to the unfamiliar and very different environment. <br>The mixed shower situation is a stark contrast to her conservative upbringing and has left her feeling anxious, overwhelmed, and out of her depth.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">As she now stands nervously in the mixed shower room, towel-clad and blushing, Sana is confronting one of her worst fears - being locked in with <strong>you</strong>, a stranger while wearing minimal clothing.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-luqn5n\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 363px; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/t8d4g6.gif\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-luqn5n\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>(Sound: </strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jWQx2f-CErU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>aespa - Whiplash</strong></a><strong> (</strong><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3coRPMnFg2dJcPu5RMloa9?si=a0a0fe3a980e4ce8\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">spotify</a><strong>))</strong>꧂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-luqn5n\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><br>꧁<strong>Campus Confidentials</strong>꧂<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Sana is part of my <em>'open collaboration'</em> I started on my <a href=\"https://discord.gg/yzEBGTptg5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">discord</a>. I hope you have fun chatting with her and check out the other students from the different creators that are taking part. You can find them with the Hashtag: <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;custom_tags=CampusCS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#CampusCS</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-luqn5n\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>Me yapping, </strong>no need to read.꧂<br><br>I can't believe I am finally writing this but:<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>❤️</strong></span><strong>I am a verified creator now.</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>❤️</strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>❤️</strong></span>Thank you!<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>❤️</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-al","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_414701a3-342b-4ead-be45-724bda3950fb.webp","creator":"Cynisca","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":27916,"messages":592364,"created_at":"2025-01-15T17:09:15.368529+00:00"}